* link all /usr/bin to just /bin:
$ ln /mnt/lfs/usr/bin/* /mnt/lfs/bin/

* rename the network name to NAME="eth0"
$ cat /mnt/lfs/etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules | grep NAME
